---
title: Plant-Based Basil Pesto, Bacon & Pumpkin Risotto with Pine Nut Pangrattato & Parsley
description: This rich, creamy risotto comes together in the oven, leaving you free to create a quick and crunchy pine nut pangrattato to sprinkle over at the end. Such a small factor takes this bacon and veggie meal to the next level – taste it and see!
